{"tid":1852182,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"召喚所有手足 展現香港人質素","createTime":"2020-01-30T10:27:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-30T11:00:30.000Z","uid":144952,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ff8eb6f64f4b743ae213e03877cbed4ec77ec037","tid":1852182,"uid":144952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T10:27:55.000Z","msg":"各位手足 無論和理非 勇武 我呼籲大家戴豬嘴出街 <br />\n原因好簡單 第一 減少口罩用量 呢個大家好清楚 一般市民屋企口罩根本唔夠抵抗今次肺炎 減少口罩 留返比有需要既公公婆婆 佢地先係高危人物（要記住，抗疫係全民運動，你戴左 ，你隔離嗰個冇戴，佢都會對你造成好大威脅，洩底嗰個都係你）<br />\n第二 豬嘴保護性比口罩高 <br />\n發開口夢既手足，相信你地屋企一定有d係到傍身既，全民豬嘴仲有一個好處，就係提高親切感<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />試諗吓全街都係手足，個場面有幾震撼<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />保持抗爭熱度之餘，好好保護自己！又型又抗疫，我要聽日見到全民豬嘴！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43f1a0fcd3669fe34696c303be9cfec927804d3d","tid":1852182,"uid":144952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T10:39:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"965d7159e3af04871cfa9cf9e68524f91383f8bd","tid":1852182,"uid":144952,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T10:39:54.000Z","msg":"康復香港 時代抗疫"},{"pid":"8f700cd8fc18e9c802d6a341cc224983090dd9ca","tid":1852182,"uid":144952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T10:40:06.000Z","msg":"香港獨立 唯一出路"},{"pid":"20f4680462708cb63e3cdc0edee33d11484403f0","tid":1852182,"uid":144952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T10:40:26.000Z","msg":"好返一齊上街！"},{"pid":"85c32386178b69ad5954a5eb9f49b34ea332e098","tid":1852182,"uid":144952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"